{"tid":2424661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「翠」字暗諷「習死兩次」？　手機遊戲角色在微博要改名","createTime":"2021-02-26T17:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T05:42:23.000Z","uid":261647,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cae2c87c647ead6dfb1fb791e394e51ed34d9ca4","tid":2424661,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Monster.Hunter.Asia/posts/3993900064009504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMonster.Hunter.Asia%2Fposts%2F3993900064009504&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=56709493\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Monster.Hunter.Asia/posts/3993900064009504</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c1QXyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c1QXyt.png&h=45a6fb43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Monster Hunter Asia 魔物獵人 遊戲資訊<br />\n<br />\n【「翠」字暗諷「習死兩次」？ 】<br />\n【中國大陸微博再掀「文字獄」】<br />\n<br />\n日前有日本手遊在大陸微博平台做宣傳時，將動漫主角名字中的「翠」字刪走，在網絡上掀起「習近平死兩次」的熱諷，有關訊息和討論迅即被封殺。評論認為，網友用隱諱方式抗議習近平惡政，而當局的過度反應顯示其內心虛怯，高壓只會激起更多民憤。<br />\n<br />\n大陸的網絡世界中，近日再掀起環繞涉及「翠」字的討論，有網友指出，「翠」字拆分後有「習死二次」之意。<br />\n<br />\nNews Credit:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/word-02252021092402.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fword-02252021092402.html&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=ad77a071\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/word-02252021092402.html</a><br />\n#翠"},{"pid":"c34d68dd241e685036bbbafacd6b36e102006e86","tid":2424661,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"呢隻字我要佢以後消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d01004fa470da1fceb9cbc0da9fc0dd7111643a","tid":2424661,"uid":74214,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:38:29.000Z","msg":"葉翠